data.description: Lovely three bedroom, two bath, Colonial  two story home in the well sought after Hill section of Latrobe. The first floor features a remodeled kitchen with shaker style maple cabinets, attractive flooring and counter tops, stainless steel appliances and recessed lighting. The large living room and dining room are perfect for family gatherings. Upstairs there are three sizeable bedrooms and a chic bathroom featuring stand alone glass and ceramic walk in shower with a separate jetted soaking tub. A large level back yard is great for outdoor activities and the covered front and back porches are great for entertaining and relaxation. Keep your car clean in the detached garage located right off the flat backyard. Convenient to local universities and hospital systems as well as the Laurel Mountains, Greensburg and the PA Turnpike.
